channel.title: My most recent music tracks
channel.description:
Hai guise, i liek 2 maek music sumtimes.
I try to mix it up every track and not repeat the same style over and over.
Here are the recent ones I like the best:
1. [url=https://www.hamsteralliance.com/music/2009/THA-impactevent.mp3][b]Impact Event[/b][/url] (Epic robot boss battle. Synths, big beats, guitars and strings. Goes into a more cinematic film score style after the 2 minute mark.)
2. [url=https://www.hamsteralliance.com/music/2009/THA-slowloris.mp3][b]Slow Loris[/b][/url] (Bass-guitar-driven something. Bass, organ, drum kit, didgeridoo, static and noise.)
3. [url=https://www.hamsteralliance.com/music/2009/THA-theendofusall.mp3][b]The End Of Us All[/b][/url] (Heavily influenced by chiptunes, but not really a chiptune itself. Has a lot of build-ups and a funky switch-up towards the end.)
4. [url=https://www.hamsteralliance.com/music/2009/THA-thefantasticalnikmis.mp3][b]The Fantastical Nikmis[/b][/url] (Electro-Classical style kind of like Hooked on Bach.)
Streaming mp3 player here: [url=https://www.hamsteralliance.com/radio/]THA Radio[/url]
Enjoy. :slight_smile:

item.title: My most recent music tracks
item.dc:creator: Hamst3r
item.description:
Hai guise, i liek 2 maek music sumtimes.

I try to mix it up every track and not repeat the same style over and over.

Here are the recent ones I like the best:

  1. Impact Event (Epic robot boss battle. Synths, big beats, guitars and strings. Goes into a more cinematic film score style after the 2 minute mark.)

  2. Slow Loris (Bass-guitar-driven something. Bass, organ, drum kit, didgeridoo, static and noise.)

  3. The End Of Us All (Heavily influenced by chiptunes, but not really a chiptune itself. Has a lot of build-ups and a funky switch-up towards the end.)

  4. The Fantastical Nikmis (Electro-Classical style kind of like Hooked on Bach.)

Streaming mp3 player here: THA Radio

Enjoy.
